{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225880/extras/long_update.gif?t=1737537281\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Here's the deal. It's the noughties, you work in a store of geek goods: games, mp3s, DVDs with movies and anime, gum, Cheetos, cigarettes, beer... Develop your store, communicate with customers (be friends, quarrel, cheat or flatter), get involved in shady dealings and earn your mom a trip to Hawaii.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">So:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\uded2 Order your favorite childhood goodies and put them on sale</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225880/extras/goods_en.gif?t=1737537281\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\udcac Choices really matter - chat with customers, bargain, count the change and cheat!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225880/extras/math_en.gif?t=1737537281\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83e\uddcd\u200d\u2642\ufe0f Keep an eye on your character's condition so you don't mess up (hunger, cold, rest - that's it)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\udcbb Play pogs with your friends to build up your collection and play mini-games on the computer</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225880/extras/games_en.gif?t=1737537281\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\udeac Go out for a smoke <span class=\"bb_strike\">and a piss</span>, there's a lot of interesting things going on outside</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\udcb0 ...mom didn't teach you to ignore strange men? Then break the law to raise money faster.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225880/extras/deeds_en.gif?t=1737537281\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Will your store become the ultimate geek spot in the town or a place to sell black market goods? The choice is yours. Go for it!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225880/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737537281","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225880/page.bg.jpg?t=1737537281","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225880/b2f65a5f88f0f92fd6186ebc2863ebfdc1f36389/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737537281","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225880/b2f65a5f88f0f92fd6186ebc2863ebfdc1f36389/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737537281","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225880/extras/long_update.gif?t=1737537281\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Here's the deal. It's the noughties, you work in a store of geek goods: games, mp3s, DVDs with movies and anime, gum, Cheetos, cigarettes, beer... Develop your store, communicate with customers (be friends, quarrel, cheat or flatter), get involved in shady dealings and earn your mom a trip to Hawaii.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">So:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\uded2 Order your favorite childhood goodies and put them on sale</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225880/extras/goods_en.gif?t=1737537281\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\udcac Choices really matter - chat with customers, bargain, count the change and cheat!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img cla